            <p>
                I’m a senior-level executive with more than 25 years of experience in finance, administration, IT, and
                human resources. I’ve worked in private and public multi-national companies across several industries,
                including:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Technology</li>
                <li>Health care </li>
                <li>Lease/asset financing </li>
                <li>Manufacturing </li>
                <li>Warehouse/distribution </li>
