        <h2 class="w-border">My Approach</h2>
        <div class="paraWrap">
            <p>No one knows your business better than you do. That’s why I will always begin by listening and asking
                questions to get a better understanding of you and your unique needs. Those insights allow me to provide
                clear, step-by-step solutions that deliver superior financial results for your business. </p>
            <p>I don’t sit by the sidelines. Instead, I can work directly with you or work with your team, either way I
